data.name: ChartTableAddressSupplier
desc: This is a helper service for access to table Address to cell ranges of the container document of a chart.
The cell addresses are in the format of the application that contains this chart.

types.name: SeriesAddresses
desc: contains the addresses to the elements of a series.
This sequence should contain one element for each series in the chart.

properties.name: CategoriesRangeAddress
desc: contains the address to the cells containing the names of the categories.
Note: Each value of a data series belongs exactly to one category.

properties.name: MainTitleAddress
desc: contains the address to the main title.

properties.name: SubTitleAddress
desc: contains the address to the sub title.
